<br>
Knights are 33 points no lances!<br>
Warriors are 14, they can get halbreds or gt weapons and come with heavy armour.<br>
Maurador horsemen are 13 points and can get a spear<br>
<br>
Magic spells, looks like only nurgle and slaanesh get new magic; everyone else gets to choose from death, fire, or shadow lores.<br>
<br>
